casebody.data:
PEOPLE
v.
SAETERN S220790 Supreme Court of California August 17, 2016

Votes: Cantil-Sakauye, C.J., Werdegar, Chin, Corrigan, Liu, Cuéllar and Kruger, JJ.

The above-entitled matter is transferred to the Court of Appeal, Third Appellate District, with directions to vacate its decision and reconsider the cause in light of People v. Franklin (2016) 63 Cal.4th 261, 268-269, 283-284, 202 Cal.Rptr.3d 496, 370 P.3d 1053. (Cal. Rules of Court, rule 8.528(d).)
